<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="D" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Delude" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Delude,</orth> to dupe: <cit><quote>thou false --ing slave,</quote> <bibl n="shak. shr 4.3.31" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. IV, 3, 31</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>O give me leave, I have --d you,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 5.4.76" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A V, 4, 76</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>let loose on me the justice of the state for thus --ing you,</quote> <bibl n="shak. oth 1.1.141" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. I, 1, 141</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>